SPEAKER 1: Well, I
think the fandom now

01:00:14.640 --> 01:00:15.870
has new marching orders.

01:00:15.870 --> 01:00:16.980
For the next four
months, you're going

01:00:16.980 --> 01:00:18.480
to get "Night Vale:
The Gathering"

01:00:18.480 --> 01:00:19.635
magic cards to your inbox.

01:00:19.635 --> 01:00:20.460
CECIL BALDWIN:
Great, let's do it.

01:00:20.460 --> 01:00:20.970
SPEAKER 1: Thank
you, Cecil so much.

01:00:20.970 --> 01:00:21.180
CECIL BALDWIN: Absolutely.

01:00:21.180 --> 01:00:21.300
Thank you so much.

